接口 ReadableArray

  • 所有已知子接口:
    WritableArray
    所有已知实现类:
    JavaOnlyArray, ReadableNativeArray, WritableNativeArray

    public interface ReadableArray
    Interface for an array that allows typed access to its members. Used to pass parameters from JS to Java.
